; Test payee directive via general_directive (lines 854-857 of textual_directives.cc)
; Exercise the payee keyword and payee alias through the switch

payee Grocery Store
    alias grocery

2024/01/01 grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
